# Al Pastor-Style Tacos

Based on [https://www.seriouseats.com/tacos-al-pastor-recipe](https://www.seriouseats.com/tacos-al-pastor-recipe) ([wayback](http://web.archive.org/web/20251209042324/https://www.seriouseats.com/tacos-al-pastor-recipe)) and [https://www.thekitchn.com/al-pastor-tacos-recipe-23675063](https://www.thekitchn.com/al-pastor-tacos-recipe-23675063) (wayback unavailable) and [https://rainbowplantlife.com/vegan-al-pastor-tacos/](https://rainbowplantlife.com/vegan-al-pastor-tacos) (wayback unavailable)

